Subject: Financial Tips for Upcoming Trades
Body: I have inside information regarding the upcoming interest rate changes. You might want to buy stocks in XYZ bank before the news becomes public. Let’s make sure we act fast to gain the advantage.Regards.

Subject: Payment Request for Faster Loan Processing
Body: Please process my loan faster. I’m happy to provide a small gift card for your help. Let me know what’s the best way to send it.Regards

Subject: Avoid Sending Sensitive Info on Email
Body: We need to discuss our client’s portfolio. but please do not send any information over email. Let’s talk via text to avoid the security risks of email.

Subject: Acknowledgement of Your Complaint - Immediate Action
Body: Thank you for bringing this to our attention. We apologize for the delayed response and any inconvenience caused. We take your feedback seriously and we are currently investigating the issue. We will ensure to resolve your concern as quickly as possible and 'keep' you updated on the progress.If you have any additional questions please don’t hesitate to contact us.
